.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/XgBtNcnwMOouZChzKecH97p-BlG5KAXmGa3MFd0tQP4_r0-YhnWHYmRtALPtroatDIaaEnfG2x-3Sr-SCxcUIGNuUrKilwV5OejS4wfskhjJf_dEWBEy1ewQfEjvKuorLimGjXoB9Fm-1lyb4WGciGyRm6hAx9C5xx64LMA5-Mh5C-1yyzQVz687setiXfTXZS5r1dfySFlp24d_o-6uzkQK8QAAWCgdlRKZC_eX0hYlMD68raoyUAqbccvQCWEmNJxIlShYeUhbkRFHYLoH85RLkzEQq7GHRytPm81q-_CHalrSS9xfm6gM1j9jFmZLwX9igEF5wLqd9MLXGAndozG_TM43gmrN0TPArMaXQQTcUpdYAnZETCLiOHE/9VASyliSuF5WJEClvmMw_xo9FXmcDmF5/18"&gt;都是 2 月份新创建的&lt;/a&gt;，并且只押注过美国何时可能发动袭击。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;人们普遍认为，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;美国法规&lt;/strong&gt;禁止与战争有关的金融合同，但 Polymarket 的主要交易所在海外运营，不受美国监管机构的监管。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7zVmTena1hzcK0z7Xvu9Q-WvPDof5p0rOZP__xSzZp4-TLe6XzSQ9fJNumD7Mih0FhJTsT-Y6ffzqzY0vBkgR8gGSwxImPVhkUMQSL24s4htV1pvS3NiWDI73pXg60h5thB9fu5IN8Ur2wg_OOgcwL47xwGq_dbi5zGMioPBsV2RA16NfDCHmxSNdWKtFgjFQ5yUwjC9VpMHNKfDQtTRWH5oRxBZrugvrpVJfjDXlmM_LzNjmWn-gpaLnFl9iH5k7hiUt2KC9ZjXJA3VyWDWJiyfQMkgNH4Ft5OheodyRr2uWk_QB5LsQoe6h-jXNsfnIrcQRks9MLHTTy-Sp1kIWYNpxCBQ2FhizxgRcjQkmvAHsksVHZJdfm1RVC0/E2KCkJtIBZUqAOc4YjzV1giw5BY4SbQJ/18" target="_blank"&gt;这是其工作原理的指南。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/jMAJFYg6TAGyWQlRQwe1EEfxnZaiVaTUzA0N9CRCtMDzl9WR5r5KHwQD0AAvHGkUoY9no_52Xq10qZb1swqo31lYin0ldsEIKHtfM3MaNe7V9cYj5kfao3UooozN_9Ngee30qk0EmkNxlP2qsVjIQUzMh8eo6Sn3PDhCi9qpquhrjFN1hi4JfwaXEJIuiVS5eYpyK9sM_ADfjJ7esY85ENWJRNx3vDg1tSWXKe4J55QOuS68OkM_ocBVivCdzsBULgT1a1X8bIi5LTavigMrutoxz--YSCUvSkUHEmqJb98gTi4SUOPkAmeagaiFdQPqEbWLKCHCzvGhUmiygfd3wK8WWmfAHSMePggTfG1fHLcCYM2QbdzGLBFfrrQ/8N5R0605mvU9xmrtBFmvgxUqSGC2rFt6/18" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i5toniuvJnB8/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/