》&lt;/em&gt;的嘉宾是&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;《歌利亚的诅咒》&lt;/em&gt;一书的作者卢克·坎普，该书从人类 5000 多年历史的兴衰中汲取了教训。阿克沙特·拉蒂 (Akshat Rathi) 问卢克，气候变化和人工智能带来的当前时刻是否使我们特别容易受到社会崩溃的影响，或者比我们想象的更有弹性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/OGTdM_fQnQKerJMz6VT9SFqIPoFIl8yyeb5jUS8m1Mo4QoA4w80Pf79tP-bqApx3VLJEyK1I34HwFtCTYtSvkzv09geWto6bn-98HU_27sGuViCHHSC5Lh6ajolvdqnzpZX2ZlVZi1UhQNKtkup6AMCw13UQPMP6jNhPHV9bF70dPHYbkAYSpygddXwJ6eYzYeW_XLf21ToiSjvEFPxjgu0L-8bbrpYbu5efRtmL6oguM2Vj0FSEZmWnfMw2yjzll0PjfjGq63zG_7bCf-0WKFz2GR8z9tPpYww2b3y3PUL6G11BdlXv2uxZk4UJ-YRhCEST0Sph7364keAD0T-9oTy_BGQySU5ssWq9zW7ETcKLzsB6gjI/MGaqy2wvDIvXydAED5atz1ksWR20Q8Sg/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="5000年历史中避免社会崩溃的教训 - 零"&gt;立即收听&lt;/a&gt;，并在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/MNRTlX2dgMDWY4pkW2I9RwRB_9nxudHArQE_2_2eZjjcmKI88cAhz1lZTxA01tmifMqg9NPp4HVXlEvbmhx52fls7vVzkq5sea_t1P5fJTbfKpgWyf2v2qUtqe7FJ3pXgzaduSoDiD8z-OkwljeM0_ldzHWSf51q4W_qmKMPYkh_A_taOlTI6uXQKqzxzmvbM3VLwKWG0-94ROBdLmSFbvAZqP4PeDSLZFm7WYFC5i2cZJBwUfDWib4eJUAIWYCE4ZXsdeglVvgHnnI786nY4yMQZPHD2kqhaw_z71EcS1R1tK-2jxoR7K9MI5JUcoOVGqrxIQ/RVHFf9_Jlyb46saAZvnzWTwqtr1TJiVG/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Omia9WAGxN7zdHKVYZLbocf1UXVT6ZAI3Uj1l3SOyvxilsBKo4thsC-6shlKZ_T_qL4fNLBt27Iq1viOqW8LhTRw_f6FuDaqErIikgud39sLAlydSErEBVz5Q5j2HVoDFa-77DBY6i-7-epSAI2RGfcH7XbbyHEXAzjE1kvNuwZXwWeUtPng0ytZVkbQhbfypIRZW9UENTXpxzRc1HP_guTYeaVXKxDxpOVbRsDdEylCs-2-j4Sjv4J79lDcOnoFu6vTqt4c6mL00cY6JCBHsvJL2gY7ujXac9ryw9Qiq5h7pZfVedH0B2HVWmX59-vrmZxtuzOcIiC2X3MmghzdXOJvwtsW/3K9GU5KuUfnouT4_87lFTW_ImEQUFtH7/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Spotify&lt;/a&gt;或&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/pNX0uwyl77CM0E36ca